dcterms:description: POJ-104 is a public dataset that contains source code solutions for algorithmic programming problems on the Peking University online judge. This dataset contains 52,000 programs, and each program is labeled with an algorithmic problem ID. In total, 104 problems are included, corresponding to a multi-class single-label classification problem with 104 classes.
dcterms:title: POJ-104

dcterms:description: ALG-109 is a newly constructed dataset that contains 11,913 pieces of source code collected from the CSDN website. Each program is labeled with the algorithms and data structures that appear in the source code, corresponding to a multi-class multi-label classification problem.
dcterms:title: ALG-109
